Package com.google.gwt.i18n.server

This package contains server-side i18n classes and interfaces.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
KeyGenerator Interface for key generation algorithms used by LocalizableResource implementations.
Message Describes a single translatable message.
MessageCatalogFactory Interface for writing various message catalog formats.
MessageCatalogFactory.Context Context for message catalogs, for things like logging errors.
MessageCatalogFactory.Writer Writes translatable messages to a message catalog.
MessageFormatUtils.TemplateChunkVisitor Visitor for template chunks.
MessageFormVisitor A visitor which is used to keep track of nesting of individual selectors and their forms within one message.
MessageInterface Describes a single interface with Messages.
MessageInterfaceVisitor Visitor that processes messages in a single class.
MessageTranslation A translation of a single message.
MessageVisitor A visitor which is used to process individual messages.
Parameter A parameter in a Messages method.
 

Class Summary
AbstractMessage Base implementation of Message.
AbstractMessageInterface Base implementation of MessageInterface.
AbstractParameter Base class for implementations of Parameter.
DefaultLanguageScripts Encodes the mapping of languages to their default script.
DefaultVisitor A default visitor implementation which does nothing and returns itself for sub-visitors.
FormVisitorDriver Keeps track of control breaks for different forms of selectors, and calls begin/end Selector/Form methods on one or more MessageFormVisitor instances when appropriate.
GwtLocaleFactoryImpl Creates server-side GwtLocale instances.
GwtLocaleImpl Class representing GWT locales and conversion to/from other formats.
KeyGeneratorAdapter Adapter to use an old-style KeyGenerator from the new API.
Message.AlternateFormMapping Mapping for a group of particular alternate forms to the message to use.
MessageFormatUtils Helper class for parsing MessageFormat-style format strings.
MessageFormatUtils.ArgumentChunk Represents an argument in a template string.
MessageFormatUtils.DefaultTemplateChunkVisitor Default implementation of TemplateChunkVisitor -- other implementations should extend this if possible to avoid breakage when new TemplateChunk subtypes are added.
MessageFormatUtils.StaticArgChunk Represents a static argument, which is used to remove markup from translator view without having to supply it at each callsite.
MessageFormatUtils.StringChunk Represents a literal string portion of a template string.
MessageFormatUtils.TemplateChunk Represents a parsed chunk of a template.
MessageUtils Utilities for processing GWT i18n messages.
PluralRuleAdapter Adapter between PluralRule and AlternateMessageSelector.
PropertyCatalogFactory Factory for GWT properties file format.
RegionInheritance Generated maps of regions into parent regions, used for locale inheritance.
Type A return type or parameter type in a Messages/Constants method.
Type.ArrayType An array type.
Type.EnumType An enum type.
Type.ListType A list type.
 

Enum Summary
MessageFormatUtils.MessageStyle Represents the style of quoting used in the source and translated messages.
 

Exception Summary
MessageFormatUtils.VisitorAbortException An exception thrown to indicate a visitor wishes to abort processing a message.
MessageProcessingException An exception during processing of i18n messages.
MessageUtils.KeyGeneratorException An exception signaling #getKeyGenerator(GenerateKeys) was unable to process the annotation.
 

Package com.google.gwt.i18n.server Description

This package contains server-side i18n classes and interfaces.
